    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, truly looking and driving as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like shine, completely free of chips, scratches, or swirl marks. Inside, the leather remains supple and the cabin retains that new-car smell, with every electronic feature and safety system functioning perfectly. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, having been meticulously maintained with a full service history and zero performance issues. For a buyer seeking a showroom-quality vehicle without the new-car depreciation, this is the perfect example.",
