    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You've seriously got to see this beauty. It\u2019s in absolute mint condition\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and it\u2019s been kept spotless inside and out. It drives like a dream and is totally ready for its next adventure. If you're looking for a ride that's practically brand new and looks stunning in the driveway, this is the one for you. Drop me a message and let's get you behind the wheel!",
      "price": 46500.0,
