    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly collector-grade vehicle that defies its age. This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, resulting in an exterior finish that remains deep, glossy, and entirely free of stone chips or swirl marks. The interior is equally impressive, retaining its original showroom scent with leather upholstery that shows no signs of creasing or wear. Every feature, from the advanced infotainment system to the tactile switchgear, operates with precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, boasting a documented history of preventative maintenance performed exclusively by master technicians. For the buyer seeking a turn-key example that looks and drives as if it just left the showroom floor, this is an unparalleled opportunity.",
      "price": 48500.0,
